data.description: Cute 3Bed 2bath 2 Car Garage home in Skies West with quick access to Albuquerque or Rio Rancho, new retail shops and restaurants, medical services and close to everything you need for convenient living. The open floorplan connects the living, dining, and kitchen areas; perfect for entertaining. Privacy-fenced back yard with open patio and low maintenance landscaping. New roof in October 2023. Come view before it's gone!!
